What am I looking at?


1010
00:49:49,386 --> 00:49:51,466
What am I seeing
right now in the sky?


1011
00:49:52,346 --> 00:49:54,946
But on the Watch, it's
alerting you when there's


1012
00:49:54,946 --> 00:49:57,016
about to be an event
in your area,


1013
00:49:57,496 --> 00:49:59,546
like the International
Space Station might be


1014
00:49:59,546 --> 00:50:01,246
about to fly overhead.


1015
00:50:02,296 --> 00:50:05,176
So they came up with a
complementary concept


1016
00:50:05,176 --> 00:50:08,946
for their App icon, and
it looks great in a circle


1017
00:50:08,946 --> 00:50:11,746
